text:
Please enhance the display of epics to be more visually compact by displaying the whole epic as a single card, with all the subtasks and their names and statuses nested inside of it. Show a progress bar for its subtasks. If there are more than three subtasks, show a "+X more" at the bottom so that the user can expand the list.)

The screenshot is from dark mode; please implement in light mode.
taskTitles: Compact epic card display with nested subtasks and progress bar
